==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lander
<hw>Land"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
lands, or makes a landing.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>lander</xex> in a
lonely isle.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>A person who waits at the mouth
of the shaft to receive the kibble of ore.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Landfall</ent>⟦br⟧
